text: Mayya Doroshko (born 23 April 1999) is a Russian synchronised swimmer. She participated at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships, winning a medal.Team technical routine results ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Russian synchronized swimmers Category:World Aquatics Championships medalists in synchronised swimming Category:Artistic swimmers at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships
